div.p:
Attributes: In addition to global attributesresp
indicates who is responsible for the interpretation.type
indicates what kind of phenomenon is being noted in the passage. Sample values include:image
(identifies an image in the passage.
   ) character
(identifies a character associated with the passage.
   ) theme
(identifies a theme in the passage.
   ) allusion
(identifies an allusion to another text.
   ) inst
points to instances of the analysis or interpretation represented
by the current element.
